title: Ive lost all my Victorious Skins????
body: Ive just recently updated league and ive had an aram game and noticed that i didnt have Victorious Morgana, i was about to make a post about it and then realize i dont have any of my Victorious skins??? Ive been Gold since Season 4 > 7 so that includes; Victorious Morgana S4, Victorious Sivir S5; Victorious Maokai S6 reward, and Victorious Graves S7. Ive attached my Lolking Rankings just as proof that ive been gold since season 4, if you dont beleive me look it up. Can anyone help me?

replies.body: The punishment for boosting or being boosted is a 14 day ban and loss of all current an previous ranked rewards. Seems likely that's what has happened.
